{"word":"διαθρυλέω","slug":"διαθρυλέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαθρυλέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>=diaqroe/w\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>mostly in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be commonly reported</i>, <el>διετεθρύλητο ὡς . .</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to be talked deaf</i>, <el>διαθρυλούμενος ὑπό σου</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}